              { "type": "intro", "text": "Two equations: a₁x + b₁y + c₁ = 0 and a₂x + b₂y + c₂ = 0" },
              { "type": "heading", "text": "Consistency Conditions" },
              { "type": "formula", "text": "a₁/a₂ ≠ b₁/b₂  → Unique solution (Consistent)\na₁/a₂ = b₁/b₂ = c₁/c₂ → Infinite solutions\na₁/a₂ = b₁/b₂ ≠ c₁/c₂ → No solution" },
              { "type": "keypoint", "text": "Elimination: multiply equations to make coefficients of one variable equal, then add/subtract." }
            ]
          },
